"bool document.isOthers(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>курсор</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsOthers</literal>, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Возвращает <literal>true</literal>, если значением атрибута символа в "
